Package org.gridgain.grid.cache.datastructures

Contains distributed data structures that work on top of data grid.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GridCacheAtomicLong This interface provides a rich API for working with distributedly cached atomic long value.
GridCacheAtomicReference<T> This interface provides a rich API for working with distributed atomic reference.
GridCacheAtomicSequence This interface provides a rich API for working with distributed atomic sequence.
GridCacheAtomicStamped<T,S> This interface provides a rich API for working with distributed atomic stamped value.
GridCacheCountDownLatch This interface provides a rich API for working with distributed count down latch.
GridCacheQueue<T> This interface provides a rich API for working with Data Grid-based distributed queues.
 

Enum Summary
GridCacheQueueType Supported distributed cache queue types.
 

Exception Summary
GridCacheDataStructureInvalidException This exception gets thrown if attempt to access an invalid data structure has been made.
GridCacheDataStructureInvalidRuntimeException This exception gets thrown if attempt to access an invalid data structure has been made.
GridCacheDataStructureRemovedException This exception gets thrown if attempt to access a removed data structure has been made.
GridCacheDataStructureRemovedRuntimeException This exception gets thrown if attempt to access a removed data structure has been made.
 

Annotation Types Summary
GridCacheQueuePriority Annotates fields or methods allowing to specify priority for queue items.
 

Package org.gridgain.grid.cache.datastructures Description

Contains distributed data structures that work on top of data grid. Distributed data structures are part of Enterprise Edition only.
